1 1 'Structure model' repository 'Initial release'        ?                 ? 
2 5 'Structure model' author     'Coordinate replacement' 'Ligand geometry' 
;Hi Team, Thank you for letting me address the ligand geometry. I refined the model again, using restrains that would keep the C38 and SG within 1.8 A. Previously that flag was not turned on during refinement. I believe the new model fully reflects the covalent adduct formed by the ligand, which has been validated in solution and is supported by the electron density, up to where the diffraction quality and resolution permits.
;
